{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_15_02",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――とある日、舞台の練習終了後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "今日はお笑いの特訓、よろしくお願いします\nうちの準備は万全です！",
      "startTime": 6.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "どんな写真でも、どんなお題でも……\nうち、最後までボケきってみせます！",
      "startTime": 12.2530814819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、俺も例の番組を研究して、傾向を掴んできた\n優の頑張りに応えられるよう、厳しくいくからな",
      "startTime": 20.0000001907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、うちのネタ、ありのまま見たまんま\n評価をして下さい！　忖度は一切なしですよ",
      "startTime": 27.2955159455,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4404.4840862,
          "startTime": 31.7000000317
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "フリップに見立てて、スケッチブックを用意したよ\n回答はこれに書いてくれ。それじゃ、いくぞ！",
      "startTime": 34.8274408076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "第一問！　「最新の冷蔵庫、この機能いらんやろ\nどんな機能？」",
      "startTime": 44.4609798994,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pen-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9505.686767299998,
          "startTime": 53.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふん……んー……閃きました！\nうちの答えは……『浴室乾燥機能』！！",
      "startTime": 53.7666668574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……冷蔵庫に、浴室乾燥機能？\nい、今一つピンとこないような……",
      "startTime": 62.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとちょっと{user}さん、そこは\nなんで冷蔵庫に浴室乾燥機能？　いらんやろ！　ですよ",
      "startTime": 68.2333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "す、すまん、俺がうまくツッコめないばかりに\nセルフツッコミをさせてしまった……",
      "startTime": 75.6666668574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "気を取り直して第二問！　「このアイドルグループは\n売れないだろうな。どんなグループ？」",
      "startTime": 82.1898676511,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pen-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3576.7990156000023,
          "startTime": 85.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　うちの答えは\n『毎回拳でセンターを決めるグループ』です！",
      "startTime": 88.4195010662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　回答のフリップの端っこに、可愛らしい絵が……\n女の子が三人？　ま、待て、あれはまさか……",
      "startTime": 96.9999966303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いやスリクスは違うからな！？　確かにそれっぽさは\nあるけど！　第一、売れてるし人気もあるから！",
      "startTime": 104.6333299636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "分かってへんなぁ、{user}さん\nほんまは売れてるからこそ……この回答は輝くんです！",
      "startTime": 110.7999964713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（一理あるけど、スリクスは世間的には仲良しってことに）\n（なってるんだぞ。際どいところを攻めるなぁ……）",
      "startTime": 119.3584059215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、{user}さん、もっとお題を下さい！\nうち、まだまだボケられます！",
      "startTime": 126.660209626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "startTime": 129.9666605948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、困ったもんや……\nまさかここまでとはなぁ",
      "startTime": 135.5333233515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "うちのお笑いのセンスに\n{user}さんはついて来れへんみたいや",
      "startTime": 140.3333233515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、最近笑えてますか？\nお笑い番組、真顔で観たりしてませんか？",
      "startTime": 147.3999900181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと笑えているから、そこは心配しないでくれ\nそうじゃなくてな、優。その……言いにくいんだけど",
      "startTime": 154.5333233515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "なんですか？　忖度はなしって言うたやないですか\n思ったことは、遠慮なく言って下さい",
      "startTime": 164.233333524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "その……優の回答は、少々玄人向けなんじゃないか？\n俺には、一般的ではないように思えるんだ",
      "startTime": 171.6666668574,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5118.474133900008,
          "startTime": 176.7851409913
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "例えばそう……\nこの写真に対するボケの内容だけど",
      "startTime": 176.5565309115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、これは会心のボケでした！　えっと……\n『瑠依ちゃんすみれちゃん、これでずーっと一緒やで』",
      "startTime": 187.3627850469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……なぜ料理の写真で、そんなセリフが出てくるんだ？\n笑えるというより、なんだか怖いんだが……",
      "startTime": 197.7666526158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　そ、そんなぁ～\nほんならこっちの写真の……",
      "startTime": 204.4666526158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "『おいおいおいっす～！　畑仕事日和やなぁ』\nこれならどうです！？",
      "startTime": 213.3666577021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "ポーズから思いついたんだろうけど、なぜ畑仕事なのか\n俺のような初心者だと、笑うより先に混乱するな……",
      "startTime": 220.6333325068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……！　あの日からずっと\n研究に研究を重ねてきたのに……",
      "startTime": 227.7333325068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "研究し過ぎて、お笑いの感覚が一般人とズレてしまった\nのかもしれないな。けして面白くない訳じゃないんだが",
      "startTime": 234.5666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、確かに沼にハマって行く感覚はありました\nうちのお笑いは、いつの間にかマニアック路線に……？",
      "startTime": 244.2666678746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "でもまぁ、ある意味目立ちそうだし、いいんじゃないか\n舞台の告知のために番組に出るんだから……",
      "startTime": 252.400001208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "……いけません、{user}さん\nそれを許したら、うちはうちでなくなってしまいます",
      "startTime": 257.6666678746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "（……そ、そんなに重大な話なのか……？）\n（このお笑いに対する情熱は、どこからくるんだ……）",
      "startTime": 265.0666678746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_02-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "うちがお笑いにハマったきっかけは、しょうもない\nダジャレで、とある人を笑わせたことがきっかけでした",
      "startTime": 272.3666678746,
      "sfxList": []
